if confirmed by the senate, o'neal would succeed david a. zegeer
since 1985, o'neal has served as deputy director of the bureau of land management at the interior department. before that he was president of o'neal inns ltd from 1984-86, president of o'neal printing, 1982-84, and executive vice president of aviation systems international from 1981-82
