while the employees were allowed to attend the caucuses, the navy said that a provision of the hatch act forbade them from speaking. some of the employees reportedly wore gags when they attended the caucuses
we are concerned that this implementation of the hatch act may have seriously affected the outcome of the caucuses in the bremerton area,'' all 10 members of the washington state delegation said in a letter to sen. john glenn, d-ohio, chairman of the senate governmental affairs committee
the committee is currently considering changes in the hatch act
